<li id="cite_note-8"><b><a href="#cite_ref-8" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web" id="CITEREFGingerich.2C_Orland1990">Gingerich, Orland (1990). <a href="http://www.gameo.org/encyclopedia/contents/W4781ME.html" class="external text" title="http://www.gameo.org/encyclopedia/contents/W4781ME.html" rel="nofollow">"Western Ontario Mennonite Conference"</a>. Global Anabaptist Mennonite Encyclopedia Online<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.gameo.org/encyclopedia/contents/W4781ME.html" class="external free" title="http://www.gameo.org/encyclopedia/contents/W4781ME.html" rel="nofollow">http://www.gameo.org/encyclopedia/contents/W4781ME.html</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2008-07-05</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Western+Ontario+Mennonite+Conference&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=Gingerich%2C+Orland&amp;rft.au=Gingerich%2C+Orland&amp;rft.date=1990&amp;rft.pub=Global+Anabaptist+Mennonite+Encyclopedia+Online&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gameo.org%2Fencyclopedia%2Fcontents%2FW4781ME.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Amish"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
