<li><a href="http://www.legalaffairs.org/issues/January-February-2005/feature_labi_janfeb05.html" class="external text" title="http://www.legalaffairs.org/issues/January-February-2005/feature_labi_janfeb05.html" rel="nofollow">The Gentle People</a>&#160;— Legal affairs article about how <a href="/wiki/Incest" title="Incest">incest</a> is handled in the Amish community</li>
<li><a href="http://missourifolkloresociety.truman.edu/Amish.htm" class="external text" title="http://missourifolkloresociety.truman.edu/Amish.htm" rel="nofollow">The Amish in Missouri, from the Missouri Folkore Society</a></li>
<li><a href="http://swartzamish.blogspot.com/" class="external text" title="http://swartzamish.blogspot.com/" rel="nofollow">First Amendment: Inside the Amish Swartzentruber sect</a></li>
<li><a href="http://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Censes_anabaptistes" class="extiw" title="fr:Censes anabaptistes">fr:Censes anabaptistes</a></li>
</ul>
